column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/eebdd998e37252da4200b2e5218b3b121292249a for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
I'm going to generalize this into adding a `getrawwallettransaction` RPC and allowing `sendrawtransaction` to do a force broadcast even if the transaction is already in the mempool.\n
